<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/20071936">为什么女人老是说男人不懂她？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="208842" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">女的说：你不懂我。<br>男的说：你不说我怎么懂你呀？<br>怎么解决这个问题？<br>男的怎么解决，让理性适应女性的感性？</div>


</div>
